articles.contents:
About Me
Hello. My name is Suvan Chatakondu and I am from Aurora,
Illinois. I am going to be a rising Senior at Metea Valley High School.
I am very interested in Statistics and Data Science and I hope to major
in something related to the field one day. I have a passion for watching
shows and movies too.
About the Project
This project is regarding a test of my Final Project.
Goals
My Goal is to learn about how to make a site for my final
project. My Goal is to make a pretty good first run so that my
final project will look nice. +However, I need to learn first.
“This is Data Science”
~Preceptor “Kane’s Free High
School Data Science Bootcamp”
